**Goal:** Replace the current text-heavy PlanCard layout with a collapsed-by-default design that uses progressive disclosure. Same content, dramatically less visual weight, premium feel.

**Files to modify:** `index.html` (PlanCard component only)

**The current problem:** PlanCards stack 6-7 pieces of information vertically at the same visual hierarchy — day, platform, hook, full caption, hashtags, posting time, and (post Change 4) the "Why this works" insight. On mobile especially, each card requires a full scroll to read. Users skim, miss key information, or fatigue out before reaching card 7.

